[12.569789, "o", "\u001b[32m▸ Searching 3 minds...\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[13.269933, "o", "\u001b[32m▸ Found 7 relevant facts (best: 0.94 similarity)\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[13.970078, "o", "\u001b[32m▸ Generating grounded response...\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[15.170214, "o", "\r\nThe Second Law of Thermodynamics states that the total\r\n"]
[15.370317, "o", "entropy of an isolated system never decreases (ΔS ≥ 0).\r\n"]
[15.570389, "o", "\r\n"]
[15.770476, "o", "Systems naturally evolve toward the macrostate with the\r\n"]
[15.970554, "o", "most microstates — this is why heat flows from hot to cold,\r\n"]
[16.17063, "o", "why ice melts, and why you can't unscramble an egg.\r\n"]
[16.370724, "o", "\r\n\u001b[2m[Grounded in: physics mind, similarity 0.94]\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[16.570805, "o", "\u001b[2m[No hallucination — answer derived from ingested knowledge]\u001b[0m\r\n"]
